section.contact-section
	h2 Contact Us
	p This is the page where you can easily email Cut, Paste &amp; Copy for questions pertaining to 
		| any projects we have done or information about our company.
		
	p To contact Cut, Paste &amp; Copy, simply leave your 
		| name, email address, and your message. We will get 
		| back to you via email in a timely manner with the 
		| answers to the questions that you have raised.  

	
	form(action="//formspree.io/nmhscutpastecopy@gmail.com" method="POST")
		label(for="name").label Enter Name: 
		input(type="text" name="name" placeholder="Enter First and Last Name").field#name
		label(for="email").label Enter Email Address: 
		input(type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter Email Address").field#email
		label(for="message").label Enter Message: 
		textarea(name="message" rows="10" placeholder="Enter Message")
		button(type="submit").submit
			i.fa.fa-paper-plane-o  Send Message
